title: Increase Cake "Staking" rewards and show the APY%
body: A great Cake Staking APY% will reduce the Cake "selling" pressure as the Cake "staking" rewards are greater or closer to the farming APY%. We may need to reduce the current 30X to 20X "farming" APY to achieve a balance here.
author: 0xdd2aD930C85151a0c3A43413703c1bAC9A77fC32
